entries.journal_entry_description: Help farmer Pol Handerin get rid of the creatures and bandits that have been plaguing his farm.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Speak with Pol Handerin, a local farmer who has been having some trouble on his farm.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Get rid of the enraged carrion spats and their leader, Gravefeather.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Eliminate the Pack of Enraged Carrion Spats
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Pol and let him know that Gravefeather and the enraged carrion spats will trouble him no more.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Nedgarr Bandits and their leader and recover the grain they stole from Pol Handerin.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Get Rid of the Bandits and Recover the Stolen Grain
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Let Pol know that the Nedgarr bandits and their leader, Trae Nedgarr, have been defeated.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Report to Lt. Jasper and let him know that you've obtained Pol Handerin's recommendation to work for his cousin at the capitol building.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Defeat Trae Nedgarr, leader of the Nedgarr Bandits.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Recover the grain the Nedgarr Bandits stole from Pol Handerin.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Defeat Gravefeather, pack leader of the enraged carrion spats.
